    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>
          What patterns do you see in <xref ref="hunds-chart"/>? Find at least 3. Color code each pattern in the chart. Describe each pattern in writing. Include a description of how to move to successive numbers and how much is added or subtracted each time you make the move. Explain why the pattern works as you say it does.
        </p>
      </statement>
    </exercise>

